     1|# Hermes WebUI - Environment Variables
     2|# Copy this to .env and customize
     3|
     4|# Ollama base URL (overrides config.yaml)
     5|# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
     6|
     7|# Additional CORS origins (comma-separated)
     8|# HERMES_CORS_ORIGINS=http://192.168.1.100:8080,http://myhost:8080
     9|
    10|# Proxy settings (for GitHub API update checks)
    11|# https_proxy=http://proxy:8080
    12|
    13|# Hermes home directory (default: ~/.hermes)
    14|HERMES_HOME=~/.hermes
    15|
    16|# DeepSeek API Key — used by model_switch for remote model routing
    17|DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=***
    18|